Package grafioschtrader.gtnet.m2m.model

Class InstrumentHistoryquoteDTO

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.gtnet.m2m.model.InstrumentHistoryquoteDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class InstrumentHistoryquoteDTO extends Object implements Serializable
DTO for historical price data of a single instrument in GTNet M2M communication. Contains instrument identification plus a list of historical price records. Instrument identification: - Security: isin + currency (toCurrency is null) - Currency pair: currency (fromCurrency) + toCurrency (isin is null)

    • forSecurityWantToReceive

      public static InstrumentHistoryquoteDTO forSecurityWantToReceive(String isin, String currency, Date wantsFromDate)
      Creates a "want to receive" response DTO for a security. Used by AC_OPEN servers to indicate interest in receiving historical data they cannot provide.
      Parameters:
      isin - the ISIN of the security
      currency - the currency of the security
      wantsFromDate - the date from which data is wanted (typically most recent local data + 1 day)

    • forCurrencypairWantToReceive

      public static InstrumentHistoryquoteDTO forCurrencypairWantToReceive(String fromCurrency, String toCurrency, Date wantsFromDate)
      Creates a "want to receive" response DTO for a currency pair. Used by AC_OPEN servers to indicate interest in receiving historical data they cannot provide.
      Parameters:
      fromCurrency - the source currency
      toCurrency - the target currency
      wantsFromDate - the date from which data is wanted (typically most recent local data + 1 day)
